{"tid":2188513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子疑沙田尾隨   女童露體遭警通緝","createTime":"2020-09-04T09:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:53:11.000Z","uid":268516,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b0107e6e96d9b2d242869bf68b6949bb8c85e8e6","tid":2188513,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"男子疑沙田尾隨女童露體遭警通緝<br />\n香港電台視像新聞 RTHK VNEWS <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/posts/3801618456612849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fposts%2F3801618456612849&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3931807e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/posts/3801618456612849</a><br />\n<br />\n警方正通緝一名約20至30歲男子，涉嫌向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為。<br />\n沙田刑事調查隊第5隊督察鍾美祺表示，昨晚8時許，兩名分別為12歲和14歲女童由沙田秦石邨行往新田圍邨方向，途經盛田街時，遇到一名中國籍男子。男子一直尾隨她們，並上前露出他的下體。兩名女童感到非常驚慌，立即離開現場，及後報警。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">警方現正通緝這名男子，身高約1.7米，中等身材，黑髮。案發時穿著黑色風衣，沒有穿褲。</span><br />\n警方提醒巿民晚上出外時，提高警覺。如有市民目擊案發過程，或遇到相似經歷應聯絡警方。<br />\n#香港電台 #沙田 #秦石邨 #新田圍邨 #猥褻"},{"pid":"622bb97e8ca7d7287f4cd09527d8ec26aa752181","tid":2188513,"uid":170365,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩標題個space會咁擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9dd5a3e7c5e1f88adeb05c2c13f91b47669365","tid":2188513,"uid":23635,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"女童露體遭警通緝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20bf9dfe6a97cbcd56679b7033fa86de366d43a","tid":2188513,"uid":68689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"捉學生就即日捉到 呢D就要人幫手捉"},{"pid":"923af0bad3d718863a7dd091573c17f3cf4fe1e7","tid":2188513,"uid":28853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1